Package: mutual
Type: Package
Title: Calculation of the Mutual Information Index
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Benjamin", "Elbers", email = "be2239@columbia.edu", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5392-3448"))
Description: Computes the mututal information index (M), a measure
    of segregation that is highly decomposable. Provides
    tools to decompose the index by units and groups (local segregation), 
    and by within and between terms. 
    Includes standard error estimation by bootstrapping.
License: GPL-3
Imports: data.table
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat
